51:25.782 --> 51:28.478
<i>"It's the tongue in our heads!</i>

51:28.552 --> 51:32.283
<i>"Listen to the truncated
bastard language of today.</i>

51:32.355 --> 51:35.256
<i>"The average vocabulary is a third
of what it was 100 years ago.</i>

51:35.325 --> 51:39.762
<i>"Words fall out of our mouths
and die at our feet!</i>

51:39.830 --> 51:42.890
<i>"The landscape of vocabulary
is being hacked down</i>

51:42.966 --> 51:46.663
<i>"and grubbed up by the dribble
of pop culture,</i>

51:46.736 --> 51:48.226
<i>"poisoned by lazy obscenity..."</i>

51:48.305 --> 51:49.363
Will?

51:49.439 --> 51:51.168
<i>"... infantilized by
a youth-obsessed media..."</i>

51:51.241 --> 51:52.936
- Hey.
- Hey.

51:53.810 --> 51:58.543
It's my favorite man-boy.
You look very manly.

51:58.615 --> 52:02.051
Well, thank you, thank you. That's the aim.

52:02.819 --> 52:05.287
- How's Emily?
- Emily.

52:06.389 --> 52:09.119
She's starring in
somebody else's diary now.

52:09.226 --> 52:10.215
